window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A Special Bonus Prequel to the Montgomery Ink Series</p> <p>The moment Shea Little walks into his shop, Shep Montgomery knows he’ll do anything to win her heart…and get into her bed. Too bad the icy shield she puts up freezes any man who comes near. Shea has her reasons, and she’s not telling anyone, not even to a man who makes her want to swoon—something she’s never done before.</p> <p>One touch can change everything; for these two, it’s only the beginning.</p>"; 
